{"tid":1504933,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"前線既手足，我地一齊黎回饋下歷史","createTime":"2019-08-25T12:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T12:16:13.000Z","uid":127735,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a6e1b968857f26ad1eef85af1f982d7f53a2c20","tid":1504933,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JqvOvqqSlFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJqvOvqqSlFg&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=5bcc88d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JqvOvqqSlFg</a><br />\n器由蛋真係基本武力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_LmPKGFhVgQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_LmPKGFhVgQ&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=84cf696d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_LmPKGFhVgQ</a><br />\n開頭一個大蛋半條防線崩左<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IY14WA-KjaI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIY14WA-KjaI&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=96c9d0d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IY14WA-KjaI</a><br />\n人多就係勝利之道<br />\n<br />\n首先場運動去到呢到，我地已經唔需要再去擔心民意，大家都已經歸曬邊。<br />\n我地宜家只係差一份勇氣，同埋武力既量。<br />\n<br />\n呢類片大家一定睇過好多次，但<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"></span></strong>聰明既你一定會睇到好多時都係示威一方人數壓制，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主攻就會嬴到</span></strong>，同埋器由蛋真係好有用，前線一定要學整。你會見到佢地警方既防線好多時都散鬆鬆，一黎可能未Set好二黎都好多火牆係到亂曬龍。<br />\n<br />\n最後想講，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">外國既警察對示威活動比香港克警有經驗得多！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港地，好多人心態都係「打份工，搵食啫」</span></strong>，克警低學歷高人工更加係，佢地唔會搵命搏。<br />\n<br />\n但相信出得黎既手足都係以命相搏，或至少有以前途相搏，因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢一仗我地一輸就輸一世</span></strong>，今時唔同往日雨傘有得翻身，一連串監控措施已經實行緊！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">當大家都放命去搏，主動出擊既時候，我好撚肯定班克警一定縮埋變粉團！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n原因有二，一佢地無外國咁有經驗只係識武力鎮壓完全無腦；二香港地打工仔心態唔會搵命搏，佢地都係肉身之軀，你敢打佢佢一樣會痛<br />\n<br />\n點都唔割<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"b02daa4ac4bb0fd384bc310b2b38fee593f04749","tid":1504933,"uid":270398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013cc595a089f2fcb0b0405e4bf01a52c99ebbc4","tid":1504933,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a4b57fbf78ed02da34a40e76f668709539b2c53","tid":1504933,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa5ba8595050d227fa8a95d8f9b2f8a7d25277fc","tid":1504933,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}